Second Department,

November, 1945.

(November 5, 1945.) Cathryn Chisholm, Respondent, v. Glad Pearl, Inc., Appellant.

Motion for reargument denied, with $10 costs. Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied. Present — Close, P. J., Hagarty, Carswell, Johnston and Lewis, JJ. [See ante, p. 943.]
